C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Iagathe, on the day of the sabbath\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>The difficulty of reading this text means that there are multiple alternative readings and some intepret the cross as a menorah and so read this as a Jewish text instead.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"NSA\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Fiorelli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Ctitle>NSA\u003C/title>\n                        \u003Cdate>1880\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>36\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Muscolino\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2011-2012\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>229 G17 fig.12\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GJKY97S8\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1961\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>197 fig.22\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/HXK7DASC\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001852\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001852\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Ferrua\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>no.474\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/759ZXHKQ\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Wessel\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>246 no. 1055\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/9CT5ZWIK\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2004-2005\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>364 fig.5\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/BMHLMJAM\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003134\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003134\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
